# Directories
.vs/
.venv/
build/
Vendor/Binaries
vcpkg/
Assets/cache

# Files
*.vcxproj
*.vcxproj.user
*.vcxproj.filters
*.sln
*.log
*.json
*.DotSettings
*.DotSettings.user
*.ini
*.cmake
CMakeCache.txt
ALL_BUILD.*
ZERO_CHECK.*
Makefile

# Local vcpkg overlay ports are real sources and MUST be committed, despite the
# blanket *.json / *.cmake ignores above (those target generated build files).
!Scripts/vcpkg-overlays/
!Scripts/vcpkg-overlays/**

# The asset registry maps the UUID handles in committed scenes to their files. It
# is project data, not build output, so it must travel with the scenes (despite
# the blanket *.json ignore) or every fresh checkout renders nothing. The demo
# content now lives in the Sandbox project, so un-ignore its registry there.
!Projects/Sandbox/assets/AssetRegistry.json

# Editor fonts are shipped assets (the NERV theme loads a monospace TTF from here).
!Assets/Fonts/
!Assets/Fonts/**
# Local user settings written by the editor on shutdown (persistent CVars). Machine-local
# state, not project data — must not be committed.
SnowstormConfig.cfg

# Neural training harness (#99): generated artifacts. Scripts under Tools/neural/ are tracked; the
# captured datasets, trained weights, and Python caches are large/generated and must not be committed.
Dataset/
*.ssnn
*.npy
__pycache__/
.pytest_cache/
